item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

As far as I know, they had a whole lot of compatibility issues with the Runetek 5 engine, as well as quite a few bugs that caused people to lose vast amounts of money (having a “drop” option on accident right under “deposit all” in the bank, which dropped the items without notifying the player and without closing the bank interface - lots of people would accidentally click this) so they probably released the fixes as soon as they could so people could start playing again.
